  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the clinical significance of gene mutations encoding antibiotic resistance, but
      not expressed as clinical resistance, in Salmonella bacteria
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Observational study. Physicians in foreign countries caring for patients with Salmonella
      meningitis or bloodstream infections will collect data on the patients they care for and
      send this data and an isolate of the organism causing the infection to the University of
      Pittsburgh.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
